	    <div class="article ">
    	    <h2><a href="/blogs/news/goodbye-cassini">Goodbye Cassini</a></h2>
        	<div class="textile">
            	<div>
<img src="https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4303/35217731293_140c5996ea_o.jpg" width="475" height="358" alt="cassini 2">

<br><br><strong>ON VIEW: September 11th to September 15th<br> GALLERY PARTY: Wednesday September 13th /// 7-11pm</strong> <br><br>
<p>The universe is full of mysteries. Black holes? Dark Matter?? Aliens??? The Cassini spacecraft has been uncovering the mysteries of the Ringed Planet, Saturn for more than a decade but now it’s almost time to end its mission with a bang... by crashing into Saturn. Come see artists move outerspace into the art space in this stellar group show.</p>
<br>Con Artist Collective &amp; Gallery<br>119 Ludlow St. New York, New York 10002<br>Open Monday through Saturday 11am to 7pm<br><br>
</div>
	        </div>
		</div>
  </div>
    
