<p><strong>Dates: September 4th to September 8th<br> GALLERY PARTY: Wednesday September 6th /// 7-11pm</strong> <br><br> Summer Residency Showcase<br> Con Artist Collective is proud to present of group exhibition of new work from our 2017 Summer Residency. Hand-picked for exceptional work in their respective mediums, this show of rising art stars is not to be missed.</p>
<p style="font-size: 18px;"><br>Featuring: <br> <a href="http://rosechebert.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Moody Rose Christopher</a><br> <a href="https://www.sahirpena.com/paintings/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sahir Pena</a><br> <a href="https://kristenleonard.carbonmade.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kristen Leonard</a><br> <a href="http://www.instagram.com/artmamaheart" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Laura Fay Lewis</a><br> <a href="http://omgitsjilliangreen.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jillian Green</a><br> <a href="http://cargocollective.com/mariaamador" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">María Amador</a><br> <a href="http://www.jakruiz.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jak Ruiz</a><br><a href="http://samallen0818.wixsite.com/storungdesign" target='_blank"'>Samuel Allen</a></p>
